### 9.1 File Storage Service

**Service:** file-service
**Endpoint:** `POST /api/files/upload`
**Purpose:** Store uploaded CSV file and error report CSV
**Timeout:** 10 seconds
**Retry Policy:** 3 attempts with exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s)
**Fallback:** Return error to user if all retries fail

---

### 9.2 Notification Service

**Service:** notification-service
**Endpoint:** `POST /api/notifications/send`
**Purpose:** Send email/SMS notification on job completion
**Timeout:** 5 seconds
**Retry Policy:** 3 attempts
**Fallback:** Log failure, do not block job completion
```

