## 11. Error Codes

| Error Code | HTTP Status | Message (English) | When |
|---|---|---|---|
| CRM_400 | 400 | Invalid file format. Expected CSV with headers. | File is not CSV or missing headers |
| CRM_401 | 413 | File size exceeds maximum allowed (10MB). | File > 10MB |
| CRM_402 | 422 | All rows in file are invalid. Please fix and re-upload. | 100% validation failure rate |
| CRM_403 | 409 | Import job already running for this upload. | Duplicate execute request |
| CRM_404 | 404 | Upload ID not found or expired. | upload_id doesn't exist |
| CRM_CUSTOMER_CODE_DUPLICATE | 422 | Customer code already exists. | Duplicate customer_code in DB |
| CRM_CUSTOMER_OWNER_INVALID | 422 | Owner user ID does not exist or is inactive. | owner_user_id FK violation |
